# Duellist
(Adapted from Pathfinder's 1e)

A master of the blade, the duellist is a master of precision and finesse. (Copilot generated comment)

**Hit Die**: d10.

### Requirements

To qualify to become a duellist, a character must fulfil all the following criteria.

**Ability Score:** Dexterity 13 or higher.

**Skills**: Acrobatics, Performance.

**Feat**: [Defensive Duelist - 5etools](https://5e.tools/feats.html#defensive%20duelist_xphb)

**Experience:** Character must be at least 5th level.

